WEBVTT

01:42.320 --> 01:45.000
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL
HIDDEN LOVE BY ZHU YI

02:03.000 --> 02:04.080
Is this okay?

02:05.080 --> 02:05.920
Yes.

02:06.640 --> 02:07.480
Thank you.

02:08.440 --> 02:11.000
Jiaxu, do you want some hangover soup?

02:11.760 --> 02:12.760
I don't drink alcohol.

02:12.840 --> 02:13.760
I don't need it.

02:14.800 --> 02:16.320
It's late. You should go to bed.

02:16.400 --> 02:18.080
I'll sleep after taking a shower.

02:19.320 --> 02:20.920
Right, Jiaxu.

02:22.120 --> 02:24.240
You need a towel

02:24.320 --> 02:26.120
and other things.

03:23.160 --> 03:25.560
Though your dad's condition is stable,

03:25.640 --> 03:27.520
we must try to avoid repeated infections.

03:27.600 --> 03:30.040
He may be sent to the ICU again
at any time.

03:32.960 --> 03:35.480
JIANG YING: CAN YOU SHOW ME
A PICTURE OF YOU IN A GRADUATION GOWN?

03:35.560 --> 03:37.040
SORRY, THAT IS AN UNREASONABLE REQUEST

03:37.120 --> 03:39.440
WHY AREN'T YOU REPLYING? ARE YOU BUSY?

03:47.920 --> 03:48.960
Why are you still up?

03:52.680 --> 03:54.600
Jiaxu, why are you still awake?

03:55.520 --> 03:56.400
I…

03:57.480 --> 03:58.560
I'm not used to this bed.

03:59.400 --> 04:00.240
I can't sleep.

04:01.800 --> 04:03.800
Then why don't I wake my brother up?

04:04.480 --> 04:06.960
You can sleep on the sofa in his room.

04:07.040 --> 04:08.520
You liked resting on that sofa

04:08.600 --> 04:10.080
during our tutoring sessions, right?

04:10.840 --> 04:11.840
It's fine.

04:11.920 --> 04:13.200
I'll go to sleep soon.

04:15.880 --> 04:17.040
It's late now.

04:17.120 --> 04:18.200
You should go to bed.

04:25.760 --> 04:27.040
Are you upset?

04:29.640 --> 04:30.800
That's not it.

04:30.880 --> 04:31.880
Why would I be?

04:40.880 --> 04:42.760
If you're upset,

04:42.840 --> 04:44.320
you can tell me about it.

04:44.880 --> 04:46.280
You might feel better afterward.

04:47.520 --> 04:49.200
I won't tell anyone about it.

04:53.960 --> 04:55.440
Not even my brother.

05:04.320 --> 05:05.840
It's fine

05:05.920 --> 05:07.600
if you don't want to talk about it.

05:09.960 --> 05:12.240
I can just keep you company for a while.

06:22.080 --> 06:23.160
Let me tell you a secret.

06:26.880 --> 06:28.000
I have

06:28.920 --> 06:31.040
plenty of debtors out there.

06:37.080 --> 06:38.720
Are you in huge debt?

06:39.880 --> 06:40.760
It isn't about money.

06:44.960 --> 06:46.760
Well, I guess it is about money.

06:50.600 --> 06:51.720
How much do you owe?

06:52.880 --> 06:53.800
Is it a huge sum?

06:56.800 --> 06:57.800
How do I put it?

07:01.000 --> 07:01.960
Jiaxu.

07:03.160 --> 07:04.480
Don't panic.

07:05.080 --> 07:06.400
Once I grow up

07:06.480 --> 07:07.720
and start making money,

07:07.800 --> 07:09.280
I'll help you pay it off.

07:18.360 --> 07:19.560
I'm not kidding.

07:19.640 --> 07:20.720
I'm serious.

07:32.920 --> 07:33.840
Sang Zhi.

07:34.720 --> 07:35.800
Actually,

07:36.520 --> 07:37.520
these aren't my debts.

07:38.360 --> 07:39.880
You don't need to help me repay them.

07:40.800 --> 07:42.120
So Sang Zhi,

07:42.200 --> 07:43.440
after you start earning money,

07:44.200 --> 07:46.360
buy some beautiful dresses for yourself.

08:28.480 --> 08:30.240
Was Jiaxu pretending to be tough?

08:31.440 --> 08:33.799
I've never seen him like this before.

09:31.240 --> 09:32.840
Make a lot of money

09:32.920 --> 09:34.520
and help him pay off his debts.

13:34.600 --> 13:37.080
JIAXU

13:41.560 --> 13:43.800
I'm taking a morning flight back to Yihe.

13:43.880 --> 13:45.640
Please tell your parents for me.

13:46.480 --> 13:48.080
Also, you should study hard.

13:48.640 --> 13:51.280
Remember to update me with your grades.

14:09.280 --> 14:10.840
Don't forget the promise

14:10.920 --> 14:11.920
you made to me.

14:15.240 --> 14:16.720
Does she mean the gifts?

14:41.720 --> 14:44.040
CHAPTER SEVEN, PROMISE

14:44.120 --> 14:46.120
THE MOST IMPORTANT LITTLE THINGS

14:47.720 --> 14:49.200
All of you are in 12th Grade now.

14:49.960 --> 14:51.160
Besides the CAP,

14:51.240 --> 14:53.040
you also need to be ready for the NCEE.

14:54.520 --> 14:55.640
This handbook

14:56.400 --> 14:58.880
contains the minimum admission scores

14:58.960 --> 15:00.680
for the nation's top schools

15:01.240 --> 15:04.200
and the corresponding
admission ratio of students

15:04.280 --> 15:06.440
from our school each year.

15:07.320 --> 15:11.280
You can compare your ranking

15:11.360 --> 15:13.200
with this handbook

15:14.000 --> 15:15.120
and make an estimation

15:15.680 --> 15:17.200
of the colleges you can select.

15:18.240 --> 15:20.360
You have to work hard for your future,

15:20.440 --> 15:21.760
move toward your goal,

15:22.240 --> 15:23.880
and enter the university of your dreams.

15:23.960 --> 15:26.400
- This is a critical moment.
- To get into Yihe University,

15:26.480 --> 15:29.480
I think I need to work harder.

15:38.960 --> 15:42.240
FIRST MOCK ASSESSMENT RESULT,
GRADE 3, CLASS 1

15:42.320 --> 15:47.240
TOP 10

15:52.440 --> 15:55.280
Jiaxu, I finally found my dream.

15:56.160 --> 15:58.080
My dream is to get into Yihe University.

16:05.800 --> 16:07.240
YIHE UNIVERSITY

16:24.680 --> 16:26.640
TOP 10

16:28.240 --> 16:31.320
SEND, PROCESSING

16:31.400 --> 16:32.240
JIAXU

16:33.920 --> 16:34.960
MAP TO MY DREAM

16:35.040 --> 16:36.200
NANWU CITY

16:36.280 --> 16:37.960
YIHE CITY

16:43.200 --> 16:44.320
MAP TO MY DREAM

16:44.400 --> 16:45.440
Twelfth place?

16:45.520 --> 16:46.480
Keep up the good work.

16:46.560 --> 16:47.720
Your gift is on the way.

16:47.800 --> 16:50.640
ENERGY CHARGING STATION

16:54.920 --> 16:56.240
YIHE, NANWU, MAP TO MY DREAM

16:56.320 --> 16:57.560
Top ten?

16:57.640 --> 16:59.040
You really did it.

16:59.120 --> 17:00.240
I've ordered your gift.

17:07.839 --> 17:10.079
YIHE CITY

17:36.880 --> 17:37.880
I must work harder

17:38.520 --> 17:40.120
and get closer

17:40.200 --> 17:41.560
to my dream.

18:02.040 --> 18:03.560
Were you rejected again?

18:07.120 --> 18:09.000
Fine, I'll stop talking.

18:09.080 --> 18:10.280
I'll stop breaking your heart.

18:13.560 --> 18:14.600
What did you say?

18:15.760 --> 18:17.880
Duan Jiaxu got himself a girlfriend?

18:19.800 --> 18:20.920
Really?

18:23.120 --> 18:25.400
Isn't that great? He has finally done it.

18:26.520 --> 18:28.080
Do you have a picture of her?

18:28.160 --> 18:29.560
Show me what she looks like.

18:30.480 --> 18:32.320
We can hold a celebration for him.

18:32.400 --> 18:33.920
I'll hang up now. I'm having supper.

18:34.000 --> 18:34.840
Bye.

18:36.880 --> 18:38.200
Sang Yan.

18:40.960 --> 18:42.600
Do you want noodles? I'll get you a bowl.

18:43.560 --> 18:45.240
Does Jiaxu have a girlfriend now?

18:45.320 --> 18:46.920
I guess so.

18:47.000 --> 18:48.320
I just heard it from Qian Fei.

18:54.520 --> 18:56.800
Hey, I got you a bowl.

19:33.160 --> 19:38.440
JIAXU, I HEARD YOU GOT A GIRLFRIEND

19:49.480 --> 19:50.720
It must be fake.

19:54.680 --> 19:56.520
It doesn't sound true.

19:58.760 --> 20:01.040
It's possible that he lied to Sang Yan.

20:03.320 --> 20:04.840
When you find one,

20:05.440 --> 20:08.160
can you show her to me first?

20:08.240 --> 20:09.640
Sure.

20:09.720 --> 20:11.880
I'll show you when I find one.

20:13.880 --> 20:14.840
I'll remember that.

20:18.080 --> 20:20.480
JIAXU

20:22.280 --> 20:23.680
You promised me.

20:26.000 --> 20:26.920
JIAXU

20:43.920 --> 20:46.480
Should I ask him in person?

21:35.680 --> 21:36.800
Hello?

21:36.880 --> 21:37.720
Hello, Sang Zhi?

21:38.280 --> 21:39.960
Why didn't you go to cram school?

21:40.040 --> 21:40.880
Look at the time.

21:42.840 --> 21:44.120
I'm in Yihe.

21:44.200 --> 21:45.560
Where?

21:45.640 --> 21:46.600
Yihe.

21:50.400 --> 21:51.440
Why did you go there?

21:53.040 --> 21:55.640
My online boyfriend told me to come.

21:56.640 --> 21:57.480
You…

21:57.960 --> 21:59.520
Which part of Yihe are you in right now?

22:01.200 --> 22:02.400
The airport.

22:03.960 --> 22:05.000
Stay there.

22:05.960 --> 22:07.360
I'll tell Duan Jiaxu to pick you up.

22:07.920 --> 22:08.760
Listen up.

22:09.320 --> 22:12.240
If you go to see
your so-called online boyfriend,

22:12.800 --> 22:14.440
you'll be in big trouble
when you get back.

22:31.800 --> 22:32.840
Hello, Dad?

22:32.920 --> 22:34.120
Have you found her?

22:34.200 --> 22:35.080
Yes.

22:36.160 --> 22:37.240
Where is she?

22:46.520 --> 22:47.440
Hello?

22:48.000 --> 22:48.840
Zhizhi.

22:49.480 --> 22:51.040
Zhizhi, didn't you promise us

22:51.120 --> 22:52.440
that you would stay away

22:52.520 --> 22:53.360
from that guy online?

22:53.920 --> 22:55.800
Stop it. Just stop.

22:55.880 --> 22:57.720
Zhizhi.

22:58.280 --> 23:00.200
Don't run around in the airport.

23:00.280 --> 23:01.600
Safety first, okay?

23:02.160 --> 23:03.160
It's best to stay in areas

23:03.240 --> 23:05.680
with airport staff and police around.

23:05.760 --> 23:07.560
If someone tries to approach you,

23:07.640 --> 23:08.840
you must go to the police.

23:08.920 --> 23:09.800
Do you understand?

23:10.560 --> 23:13.840
By the way, Sang Yan
will tell Duan Jiaxu to pick you up.

23:13.920 --> 23:15.080
Be nice, okay?

23:20.080 --> 23:22.800
Mom, Jiaxu is calling me.

23:23.520 --> 23:25.160
Okay. Be careful.

23:34.000 --> 23:34.920
Hello?

23:35.000 --> 23:36.040
Where are you?

23:38.320 --> 23:39.400
Exit 18.

23:40.160 --> 23:41.120
Okay.

23:53.080 --> 23:54.280
Sang Zhi!

23:57.120 --> 23:58.000
Jiaxu.

24:02.080 --> 24:03.160
Have you found her?

24:39.200 --> 24:40.280
Didn't you promise me

24:41.480 --> 24:42.600
that you would study hard

24:42.680 --> 24:43.960
and wouldn't make others worry?

24:45.920 --> 24:47.240
Online boyfriend?

24:50.520 --> 24:52.240
Have you forgotten what I told you before?

24:53.320 --> 24:54.600
You're all grown up now, are you?

24:55.240 --> 24:57.320
How dare you travel so far by yourself?

25:00.440 --> 25:01.560
Who is she?

25:03.600 --> 25:05.040
Is she your girlfriend?

25:08.000 --> 25:10.640
You promised to tell me first.

25:11.920 --> 25:13.920
Why didn't you keep your promise?

25:17.040 --> 25:18.240
Say something.

25:21.640 --> 25:22.520
Jiaxu.

25:23.080 --> 25:24.600
Don't speak so harshly to her.

25:51.000 --> 25:52.360
Did he tell you to come?

25:58.440 --> 25:59.640
Have you met him?

26:04.560 --> 26:06.040
He doesn't like me.

26:11.120 --> 26:12.680
He said that I'm too young.

26:22.280 --> 26:23.280
Has he left?

26:31.080 --> 26:32.280
Sang Zhi.

26:32.360 --> 26:33.760
He did the right thing.

26:34.520 --> 26:36.200
You're too young right now.

26:36.280 --> 26:37.760
This isn't right. Got it?

26:39.600 --> 26:41.200
But I will grow up.

26:41.280 --> 26:43.320
Then let's wait until you grow up.

26:43.880 --> 26:44.840
But when I grow up,

26:44.920 --> 26:46.360
he'll fall for someone else.

26:56.520 --> 26:57.440
That's fine.

26:59.720 --> 27:01.400
Sang Zhi, when you grow up,

27:03.240 --> 27:04.440
you will meet someone better.

27:05.880 --> 27:07.080
I guess this lady

27:08.360 --> 27:10.640
is your "someone better."

27:26.720 --> 27:27.640
Sorry.

27:30.520 --> 27:31.840
Sorry for troubling you.

27:32.920 --> 27:34.400
I won't do this again.

27:38.480 --> 27:40.200
You're no trouble.

27:53.360 --> 27:54.320
Wipe your tears.

27:56.200 --> 27:58.000
We were worried about you.

27:58.800 --> 28:01.360
We were scared
that something might happen to you.

28:02.640 --> 28:03.920
But now,

28:04.000 --> 28:05.880
it's good that you realize your mistake.

28:09.320 --> 28:10.520
Wash up in the restroom.

28:11.680 --> 28:12.800
I'll take you out to lunch.

28:12.880 --> 28:13.840
I don't feel like going.

28:14.600 --> 28:15.720
I want to go home.

28:15.800 --> 28:17.240
Even so, you need to eat first.

28:18.120 --> 28:19.720
Give me your ID card.

28:19.800 --> 28:21.240
I'll get a plane ticket for you.

28:21.320 --> 28:24.200
Jiaxu, why don't I take her?

28:25.440 --> 28:26.680
It's fine, miss.

28:26.760 --> 28:28.040
I can go by myself.

28:28.520 --> 28:30.200
I can take care of myself.

28:35.680 --> 28:36.840
Here, get up.

28:39.600 --> 28:41.280
The restroom is over there.

28:41.360 --> 28:42.480
Go and wash your face.

28:43.880 --> 28:45.560
I'll go get lunch with you

28:45.640 --> 28:46.880
after buying your plane ticket.

28:51.800 --> 28:52.720
Go now.

28:54.200 --> 28:56.200
We'll have a nice lunch.

29:06.760 --> 29:08.080
The kiddo is all grown up.

29:49.480 --> 29:50.600
So different from before.

29:53.960 --> 29:55.840
That's how young girls are.

29:55.920 --> 29:57.200
They'll grow up eventually.

29:57.280 --> 29:58.440
Don't be too worried.

31:30.520 --> 31:32.640
Why did you take it off? Put it on.

31:32.720 --> 31:33.680
I don't need it.

31:35.200 --> 31:36.800
Where's the lady?

31:38.080 --> 31:39.400
She's busy and had to leave.

31:45.400 --> 31:47.880
Was I too harsh earlier?

31:55.600 --> 31:57.120
Kids are forgetful indeed.

31:58.080 --> 31:59.400
You're treating me like a stranger

31:59.480 --> 32:00.960
after a few months away.

32:02.120 --> 32:03.640
I'm pretty heartbroken.

32:06.280 --> 32:08.120
How much was the plane ticket?

32:10.800 --> 32:11.800
It didn't cost a lot.

32:12.760 --> 32:13.920
The flight is at 1:10 p.m.

32:14.000 --> 32:15.120
We still have some time.

32:15.200 --> 32:16.400
I'll take you to eat something.

32:18.200 --> 32:19.440
Let's go.

32:28.720 --> 32:29.600
Eat something.

32:43.400 --> 32:44.680
Are you sick?

32:46.440 --> 32:48.520
No, it's just a cold.

32:52.760 --> 32:54.080
I'm fine.

32:54.160 --> 32:55.360
Are you really not eating?

33:07.440 --> 33:08.640
It's a gift for you.

33:09.480 --> 33:10.520
For me?

33:17.680 --> 33:18.920
Can I open it?

33:29.440 --> 33:31.080
So you still remember me.

33:33.440 --> 33:34.560
I love your gift.

33:35.520 --> 33:36.360
Thank you.

33:45.920 --> 33:46.960
I'm going to take this.

33:53.120 --> 33:54.120
I've picked her up.

34:44.520 --> 34:45.440
All right.

34:55.440 --> 34:58.000
Listen to your parents after you get home.

34:58.760 --> 35:01.080
Don't let this affect your studies.

35:02.160 --> 35:03.120
Okay?

35:06.400 --> 35:08.320
You don't need to tell me anymore.

35:13.720 --> 35:14.600
What?

35:17.120 --> 35:18.800
You don't need to tell me anymore

35:20.440 --> 35:21.880
if you get a girlfriend.

35:55.120 --> 35:57.120
Isn't this the bear plushie I got for you?

36:01.880 --> 36:02.960
It's for you.

36:06.720 --> 36:07.640
I wish you

36:08.520 --> 36:09.640
happiness every day.

36:12.160 --> 36:13.960
You must stay happy too.

36:19.440 --> 36:20.680
I'm going now.

36:20.760 --> 36:21.880
Bye.

36:43.040 --> 36:43.880
Go now.

38:45.000 --> 38:45.840
Little demon.

39:05.480 --> 39:07.360
Forget it. I'll spare you this time.

39:07.440 --> 39:08.280
Let's go home.

39:09.680 --> 39:12.080
Mom already told your private tutor
to take the day off.

39:12.560 --> 39:14.320
But I can't help you

39:15.040 --> 39:16.360
if Mom and Dad scold you later.

39:26.120 --> 39:27.160
If so…

39:30.320 --> 39:31.160
If so…

39:33.920 --> 39:35.360
How about this?

39:35.440 --> 39:37.640
I'll buy you a crispy taro-crusted duck.

39:39.600 --> 39:40.440
But…

39:41.480 --> 39:43.560
All right now.

39:46.280 --> 39:47.840
It's just heartbreak.

39:47.920 --> 39:49.440
It's not a big deal.

39:54.240 --> 39:56.680
I'll buy you the last several volumes

39:56.760 --> 39:57.880
of the comic you read, okay?

40:00.920 --> 40:02.040
How about this then?

40:02.120 --> 40:04.960
I'll find someone to beat him up, okay?

40:07.560 --> 40:08.800
Not that either?

40:11.520 --> 40:12.880
Good girl. I'm here for you.

40:12.960 --> 40:14.680
I'm here for you.

40:14.760 --> 40:16.400
Don't cry, okay?

40:24.960 --> 40:25.920
It's okay.

40:42.720 --> 40:43.560
You're back.

40:58.120 --> 41:00.120
What's wrong? Are you cold?

41:00.200 --> 41:01.560
Put on something thicker.

41:01.640 --> 41:02.680
Wash up and come to dinner.

41:04.880 --> 41:06.400
Go and get changed first.

41:08.120 --> 41:09.080
It will be fine.

42:17.240 --> 42:18.600
I know you're heartbroken.

42:19.480 --> 42:20.680
But I need to remind you

42:20.760 --> 42:22.400
of the severity of the situation.

42:22.480 --> 42:24.480
Do you know how worried Mom and Dad were?

42:32.280 --> 42:33.600
All right, little demon.

42:33.680 --> 42:35.840
At your age, you should study hard.

42:35.920 --> 42:37.840
Do not get into puppy love.

42:37.920 --> 42:39.360
Besides,

42:39.440 --> 42:41.240
you stole an ID card
to buy a plane ticket.

42:41.320 --> 42:43.440
What if you had encountered a bad guy?

42:47.000 --> 42:48.720
Stop playing dead. Give me a nod.

42:58.480 --> 43:00.320
There was no online boyfriend.

43:01.800 --> 43:03.360
I just wanted to ask him

43:04.680 --> 43:05.840
whether he remembered

43:06.920 --> 43:08.320
our promise.
